<common:UserControlBase
    x:Class="Zappos.UserControls.MeetTheTeam"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:local="using:Zappos.UserControls"
    xmlns:common="using:Zappos.Common"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    mc:Ignorable="d"
    d:DesignHeight="768"
    d:DesignWidth="1366">
	
	<common:UserControlBase.Resources>

		<Style x:Key="ImageStyle" TargetType="Image">
			<Setter Property="Stretch" Value="None"/>
			<Setter Property="HorizontalAlignment" Value="Center"/>
			<Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Bottom"/>
		</Style>

		<Style x:Key="JobTitleTextBlockStyle" TargetType="TextBlock">
			<Setter Property="Foreground" Value="#000000"/>
			<Setter Property="FontSize" Value="18"/>
			<Setter Property="LineHeight" Value="20"/>
			<Setter Property="HorizontalAlignment" Value="Left"/>
			<Setter Property="VerticalAlignment" Value="Bottom"/>
		</Style>

		<Style x:Key="QuoteBorderStyle" TargetType="Border">
			<Setter Property="Background" Value="#99000000"/>
			<Setter Property="CornerRadius" Value="10"/>
		</Style>
		
		<Style x:Key="QuoteRichTextBlockStyle" TargetType="RichTextBlock">
			<Setter Property="FontSize" Value="20"/>
			<Setter Property="LineHeight" Value="22"/>
			<Setter Property="Foreground" Value="#FFFFFF"/>
			<Setter Property="Margin" Value="20,20,20,0"/>
		</Style>
		
		<Style x:Key="QuoteCloseButtonStyle" TargetType="Button">
			<Setter Property="Content" Value="Close"/>
			<Setter Property="HorizontalAlignment" Value="Right"/>
			<Setter Property="Margin" Value="20,0,20,20"/>
		</Style>

		<Storyboard x:Name="HideRonQuote">
			<PopOutThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="RonQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>
		<Storyboard x:Name="ShowRonQuote">
			<PopInThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="RonQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>

		<Storyboard x:Name="HideKevinQuote">
			<PopOutThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="KevinQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>
		<Storyboard x:Name="ShowKevinQuote">
			<PopInThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="KevinQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>

		<Storyboard x:Name="HideJamesQuote">
			<PopOutThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="JamesQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>
		<Storyboard x:Name="ShowJamesQuote">
			<PopInThemeAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="JamesQuote"/>
		</Storyboard>

	</common:UserControlBase.Resources>

	<Grid Background="#FFFFFFFF">
		<Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<RowDefinition Height="180"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="100"/>
			<RowDefinition Height="*"/>
		</Grid.RowDefinitions>
		<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="3.33*"/>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="3.33*"/>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="3.33*"/>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
		</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
		<TextBlock Text="Meet the CSG Management Team" Style="{StaticResource DetailPageTitleStyleLight}" 
				   Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="3"/>
		<TextBlock x:Name="RonJobTitle" Text="Ron Ellis Gaut&#10;Director&#10;Consulting" Style="{StaticResource JobTitleTextBlockStyle}"
				   Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="2" Margin="0,40,0,320"/>
		<TextBlock x:Name="KevinJobTitle" Text="Kevin McVicker&#10;President" Style="{StaticResource JobTitleTextBlockStyle}"
				   Grid.Column="2" Grid.Row="2" Margin="-10,40,0,360"/>
		<TextBlock x:Name="JamesJobTitle" Text="James Churchill&#10;Practice Mgr&#10;App Dev" Style="{StaticResource JobTitleTextBlockStyle}"
				   Grid.Column="3" Grid.Row="2" Margin="0,40,0,330"/>
		<Image x:Name="RonPhoto" Source="/Assets/RonPhoto.png" Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="2" 
			   Style="{StaticResource ImageStyle}" Tapped="RonPhoto_Tapped_1"/>
		<Image x:Name="KevinPhoto" Source="/Assets/KevinPhoto.png" Grid.Column="2" Grid.Row="2" 
			   Style="{StaticResource ImageStyle}" Tapped="KevinPhoto_Tapped_1"/>
		<Image x:Name="JamesPhoto" Source="/Assets/JamesPhoto.png" Grid.Column="3" Grid.Row="2" 
			   Style="{StaticResource ImageStyle}" Tapped="JamesPhoto_Tapped_1"/>
		<Border x:Name="RonQuote" Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="2" Grid.ColumnSpan="3" Style="{StaticResource QuoteBorderStyle}" Visibility="Collapsed" 
				HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Width="600" Height="240" Margin="-40,0,0,20">
			<StackPanel>
				<RichTextBlock Style="{StaticResource QuoteRichTextBlockStyle}">
					<Paragraph>
						As a founding member of the CSG team with 20 years of history, there are a few really noteworthy engagements 
						that stand out from all the rest. Developing this e-commerce app for Zappos feels like one of those and I am 
						excited about that. It is the kind of project we live for (and our developers fight over). If given the chance 
						to build this app, you get the very best CSG has to offer. Thanks for your consideration!
					</Paragraph>
				</RichTextBlock>
				<Button x:Name="CloseRonQuoteButton" Click="CloseRonQuoteButton_Click_1" Style="{StaticResource QuoteCloseButtonStyle}"/>
			</StackPanel>
		</Border>
		<Border x:Name="KevinQuote" Grid.Column="2" Grid.Row="2" Grid.ColumnSpan="3" Style="{StaticResource QuoteBorderStyle}" Visibility="Collapsed" 
				HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Width="800" Height="240" Margin="-200,0,0,20">
			<StackPanel>
				<RichTextBlock Style="{StaticResource QuoteRichTextBlockStyle}">
					<Paragraph>
						The <Run FontWeight="Bold">Zappos Family Core Values</Run> really align with CSG Pro and with me personally. 
						Our stated goals are Do What's Right, Deliver Excellence, Team Over Self, and Create Value. We do our best to 
						live this out in every client relationship and it is really easy when the client is after the same things. 
						It looks like this would be our experience with Zappos and we would have a lot of fun along the way. Please feel 
						free to call me if you have any questions or just want to chat. We are excited about the opportunity to work together.
					</Paragraph>
				</RichTextBlock>
				<Button x:Name="CloseKevinQuoteButton" Click="CloseKevinQuoteButton_Click_1" Style="{StaticResource QuoteCloseButtonStyle}"/>
			</StackPanel>
		</Border>
		<Border x:Name="JamesQuote" Grid.Column="3" Grid.Row="2" Grid.ColumnSpan="3" Style="{StaticResource QuoteBorderStyle}" Visibility="Collapsed" 
				HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Width="700" Height="240" Margin="-280,0,0,20">
			<StackPanel>
				<RichTextBlock Style="{StaticResource QuoteRichTextBlockStyle}">
					<Paragraph>
						I was there at Microsoft's 2011 Build Conference when Windows 8 was announced. Developers across the world 
						(myself included) were excited about the possibilities that Windows 8, and in particular the Windows Store, 
						represented. Getting companies like Zappos.com onto the Windows 8 platform will be critical to the Windows Store's 
						overall success. I hope that CSG Pro gets an opportunity to help make Zappos.com's Windows Store application 
						a reality.</Paragraph>
				</RichTextBlock>
				<Button x:Name="CloseJamesQuoteButton" Click="CloseJamesQuoteButton_Click_1" Style="{StaticResource QuoteCloseButtonStyle}"/>
			</StackPanel>
		</Border>
	</Grid>
</common:UserControlBase>
